Package: simsmolt
Type: Package
Title: simulate Atlantic salmon smolt migration and detections on acoustic arrays
Version: 0.1.0.9203
Date: 2021-02-09
Author: Ian Jonsen
Maintainer: Ian Jonsen <ian.jonsen@mq.edu.au>
Description: simulate salmon smolt migration as compound biased random walks with or without advection, simulate acoustic tag transimissons and detections along migration paths, conditional on real or simulated accoustic reciver arrays
Depends: R (>= 3.5.2)
